content:
IWithPublicFrontend Interface

Definition

The stage of an Internet-facing load balancer definition allowing to define one or more public frontends.

In this Article

public interface IWithPublicFrontend

Methods

DefinePublicFrontend(String)

Begins the definition of a new load public balancer frontend. The definition must be completed with a call to LoadBalancerPublicFrontend.DefinitionStages.WithAttach.attach().
